channel.title: Need A server Coded? I'm your man!
channel.description:
Well, I have made a lot of RS2 servers and I have decided instead of making my own custom servers i could code someones else for them... Well. Basically i need you to reply with this form.
[code] [b]Desired Server Name:[/b] [b]Desired Server Source:[/b] [b]Features You want?:[/b] [/code] Thats basically the required part of the form. Feel free to add in Different things.
